	<h2>About</h2><p>Welcome to the Minds Alpha Project. Our mission is to organize the world's free and open information.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Minds is open source social media. We are a universal and decentralized to search, create and share information.&nbsp; Site evolution is based on global voting and contributions of the people.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Everything created &amp; shared here is free for the world to download and remix under a variety of free, open source and creative commons licenses.&nbsp; This includes video, audio, images, text, code, software, files, apps, etc..&nbsp; When you upload into Minds you are contributing to the freedom of information, speech &amp; press worldwide!&nbsp;</p>
